  "texts": [
    "For some LC types, we detected a reliable response to only one or a few stimuli (e.g., LC15 only responded to 'vary female position' and 'natural sequence').",
    "We noticed that none of the LC neurons responded to stimulus sequences for which the fictive female's parameters were chosen to optimize the 1-to-1 network's output of lateral velocity ('optimize lateral vel.'",
    "and 'optimize lateral vel.",
    "(fast)', see Methods).",
    "This may be due to the fast changes in female position which were not present in other stimulus sequences."
  ],
